    "summary": "The user attempts to query the impacts of a hypothetical or misnamed \"2024 tax reform\" on wealth inequality. After clarifying the timeline, the user prompts the assistant to explain the different economic perspectives on the tax changes. The assistant ultimately rejects the user's request for balance, instead asserting a consensus that invalidates the opposing viewpoint.",
